# Agent Context Snapshot

Before substantial work, take a quick snapshot of current agent activity:
- Check what other agents are actively running and their current task.
- Check recently completed agent outputs/transcripts for relevant context.
- Use this snapshot to avoid duplicate work and align with in-flight changes.
- Keep this check lightweight and proceed immediately after the snapshot.
